OL,3,CThomas Partey enters not guilty pleas
OL,4,Cto two new rape allegations
OL,6,FFormer Arsenal footballer Thomas
OL,7,FPartey has pleaded not guilty to two
OL,8,Fnew allegations of rape.
OL,10,FThe 32-year-old midfielder appeared at
OL,11,FSouthwark Crown Court on Monday to
OL,12,Fdeny twice raping a woman in London on
OL,13,Fa day in December 2020.
OL,15,FThe star, who left Arsenal for
OL,16,FVillarreal last summer, was charged in
OL,17,FJuly last year with five counts of
OL,18,Frape and one allegation of sexual
OL,19,Fassault, dating back to 2021 and 2022.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
