OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776164568
OL,3,CThomas Partey enters not guilty pleas
OL,4,Cto two new rape allegations
OL,6,FHe previously pleaded not guilty to
OL,7,Fthose charges, and a trial was set for
OL,8,FNovember this year.
OL,10,FThe two new rape charges were
OL,11,Fannounced in February this year, and
OL,12,Fon Monday Judge Tony Baumgartner, the
OL,13,FRecorder of Westminster, agreed for
OL,14,Fall the allegations to be tried
OL,15,Ftogether.
OL,17,FBut he warned Partey and lawyers in
OL,18,Fthe case that the trial could now be
OL,19,Fdelayed until January next year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
