OL,3,CThomas Partey enters not guilty pleas
OL,4,Cto two new rape allegations
OL,6,FIn total, the footballer has now
OL,7,Fpleaded not guilty to seven counts of
OL,8,Frape and one count of sexual assault,
OL,9,Frelating to allegations from four
OL,10,Fdifferent women.
OL,12,FPartey, wearing dark grey trousers, a
OL,13,Fblack jumper over a white shirt, and
OL,14,Fsmart black shoes, spoke to confirm
OL,15,Fhis name and enter the two not guilty
OL,16,Fpleas during Monday's hearing.
OL,18,FHe left the dock with his charcoal
OL,19,Fgrey suit jacket slung over his left
OL,20,Fshoulder.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
