OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776164568
OL,3,CThomas Partey enters not guilty pleas
OL,4,Cto two new rape allegations
OL,6,FPartey was absent from Westminster
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court last month when the
OL,8,Fcharges came before a judge for the
OL,9,Ffirst time.
OL,11,FBut his lawyer indicated that not
OL,12,Fguilty pleas would be entered.
OL,14,FThe Ghanaian midfielder, who
OL,15,Fpreviously lived in Potters Bar in
OL,16,FHertfordshire, joined Arsenal from
OL,17,FAtletico Madrid in 2020 in a transfer
OL,18,Fworth around #45 million, before he
OL,19,Fleft the club in June last year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
