OL,3,CThomas Partey enters not guilty pleas
OL,4,Cto two new rape allegations
OL,6,FHe is expected to face England in the
OL,7,FWorld Cup this summer, as an integral
OL,8,Fpart of the Ghana national side.
OL,10,FPartey is on bail during the legal
OL,11,Fproceedings, with a condition that he
OL,12,Fdoes not contact alleged victims.
OL,14,FThe court heard Mr Justice Bennathan
OL,15,Fis expected to be the trial judge.
OL,17,FPartey's case is next due to be listed
OL,18,Fin court, for a pre-trial hearing, on
OL,19,FMay 14.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
